{
  "texts": [
    "We received IRB approval (IRB23-0454) prior to conducting the task.",
    "All participants provided informed consent and were compensated for their time.",
    "Because participants had real-time interactions with either humans or GPT we decided not to use the prior results for our preregistered power analysis.",
    "Instead, we reviewed the literature to find cases where human emotional support was compared to that of AI.",
    "One such paper is a recent paper by Yin and colleagues (Yin et al., 2024),"
  ]
}